#admin
  nav.fixed.top.wide.flex.justify-space-between.padding-x-small.shadow.z-nav(style="min-height: 5rem")
    //- Left Side
    div.flex
      //- Hamburger Menu
      .menu.hide-large.center-child
        a.padding.inline-block(href="#" @click="EventBus.$emit('toggle', 'home-drawer')")
          fa(icon="bars")
      //- Nav Logo
      .logo.show-medium-plus.center-child.padding-x-medium
        strong Admin Console
      //- Navigation Links
      ul.links.remove-list-style.show-large.flex.center-child-child
        each val, index in {'Dashboard':'/admin/dashboard','Transactions':'/admin/transactions','Settings':'/admin/settings','Reports':'/admin/reports'}
          li
            router-link.padding(to=val :class="{'active': $route.path.includes('"+val+"')}")=index
    //- Right Side
    div.flex.center-child
      notification-button
      router-link.padding(to="/")
        span.margin-right-small Exit Console
        fa(icon="sign-out-alt")

  router-view
